QuestData.Title: Chipping In
QuestData.Description: As you have no doubt noticed by now, the recent changes to the land have had many side-effects. Some of these are beneficial, while others pose serious problems.$b$bJust south of the village the local lobstrok are emerging from the sea and choking off the road to the village.$b$bPlease, $c, go and thin the numbers of this pest.
QuestData.LogDescription: Kill 5 Drysnap Crawlers and 5 Drysnap Pincers.
QuestData.CompletionText: Has our lobstrok problem been dealt with, $c?
QuestData.RewardText: On behalf of us all at Shadowprey Village, I thank you, $r.
